        "Privacidad1": "In accordance with the provisions of Article 19 No. 4 of the Political Constitution of the Republic and the relevant rules of Law No. 19,628 on protection of privacy and its subsequent amendments, the processing of personal data that is performed in https://visitacolbun.cl/ as part of the office of Culture and Tourism of the Municipality of Colbún, is governed by the following rules:",
        "Privacidad2": "The Municipality of Colbún through the office of Culture and Tourism ensures the confidentiality of personal data of users who register as such on the website https://visitacolbun.cl/ through the form (s) established for this purpose. Without prejudice to its legal powers, the Municipality of Colbún through the office of Culture and Tourism will only process personal data with respect to those that have been voluntarily submitted by users in the aforementioned form.",
