        "HotSprings": "Hot Springs",
        "HotSpringsInfo": "The hot springs within the commune of Colbún are renowned for their mineral-medicinal waters, which have curative properties and have been declared as such by the Ministry of Health since 1946. The thermal centers (Termas de Panimávida and Termas de Quinamávida) offer various facilities, including heated pools and a spa with beauty treatments, all in a natural environment that invites disconnection and relaxation. In addition, visitors can enjoy recreational activities for the whole family, as well as gastronomic options that complement the experience.",
