        "WatchNow": "Watch Now",
        "ColbunAltoRemember": "Discover Colbún Alto, a place with a unique combination of nature and adventure. In this area, you can explore the trails that cross the green hills, enjoy the waters of Lake Colbún, and immerse yourself in the charm of rural life. Colbún Alto invites you to live unforgettable experiences, immersed in the serenity of a majestic natural environment and the warm sense of community that characterizes the towns of our commune.",
