        "Test3": "Test 3",
        "ColbunAltoInfo": "Colbún Alto is a charming town. It stands out for its panoramic views of the majestic landscapes and its proximity to Lake Colbún. In Colbún Alto, the tranquility of rural life combines with the majesty of nature, offering visitors the opportunity to enjoy outdoor activities such as hiking, fishing and bird watching. This town is ideal for those looking to escape the urban bustle and immerse themselves in a serene and natural environment, where the local community keeps alive the traditions and welcoming spirit of the Chilean countryside.",
        "ComeCloser": "Come closer to",
        "OurCommunity": "our community",
        "ColbunServiceCountry": "Colbún Service Country and the Municipality of Colbún share their transformative experiences in the various localities of the commune. Dive into their stories, from the revitalization of public spaces to social inclusion projects that have improved the quality of life of neighbors. From educational workshops in rural areas to the promotion of local entrepreneurship, discover how working together has made a difference in the heart of Colbún.",
        "Collaboration": "Discover how collaboration can transform communities",
